---
const siteUrl = 'http://localhost:4321';
const imageUrl = `${siteUrl}/preview.png`;
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Preview Image Test</title>
  <style>
    body {
      background: #000;
      color: white;
      font-family: system-ui;
      padding: 40px;
      max-width: 1400px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .test-card {
      background: #1a1a1a;
      border: 2px solid #2FB7B8;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 30px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #2FB7B8;
    }
    img {
      max-width: 100%;
      border: 2px solid #2FB7B8;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .success {
      color: #2FB7B8;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .info {
      color: #ccc;
      margin: 10px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>üñºÔ∏è Preview Image Test</h1>
  
  <div class="test-card">
    <h2>Direct Image Load Test</h2>
    <p class="info">Testing if preview.png loads correctly:</p>
    <img src="/preview.png" alt="Preview Image" />
    <p class="success">‚úì If you see an image above, preview.png is working!</p>
  </div>

  <div class="test-card">
    <h2>Meta Tags Test</h2>
    <p class="info">Image URL being used in meta tags:</p>
    <code style="color: #2FB7B8; background: #000; padding: 10px; display: block; border-radius: 4px;">
      {imageUrl}
    </code>
  </div>

  <div class="test-card">
    <h2>File Information</h2>
    <p class="info">Path: <code style="color: #2FB7B8;">/public/preview.png</code></p>
    <p class="info">Expected dimensions: 1200 √ó 630 (or close to it)</p>
    <p class="info">Actual dimensions: 1200 √ó 646</p>
  </div>

  <div class="test-card">
    <h2>Next Steps</h2>
    <ol style="line-height: 1.8;">
      <li>If the image loads above, your preview.png is working correctly ‚úì</li>
      <li>Go to <a href="/preview-test" style="color: #2FB7B8;">preview-test page</a></li>
      <li>Do a hard refresh: <strong>Cmd+Shift+R</strong> (Mac) or <strong>Ctrl+Shift+R</strong> (Windows)</li>
      <li>All pages should now show the preview.png image</li>
    </ol>
  </div>

  <div class="test-card">
    <h2>Still Not Working?</h2>
    <p>Try these steps:</p>
    <ul style="line-height: 1.8;">
      <li>Open preview-test in an <strong>incognito/private window</strong></li>
      <li>Clear your browser cache completely</li>
      <li>Restart the dev server</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
